						<summary>

						<p>A fourth fragment built into the same wall.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">No king: No date.</hi></p>						

						<p>This piece of an inscription is too fragmentary, and the passage preserved here contains only the last part of the record. It refers to certain privileges like the <hi rend="italic">viḷakkeṇṇai-bhōgam, tiruvamudu-bhōgam, mañjaḷ-iñji,</hi> etc.</p>						

